{"id":522373,"date":[{"year":1972,"month":10,"day":15}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"196","ytitle":"","mtitle":"乡邮员","ftitle":"","authors":["胡天麟"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡邮员，年十八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色邮路添新花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背起绿包辫一甩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身披风尘走千家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若问肩头负多重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里江山万里画!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父辈嘱托记心头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨中英姿更焕发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀坡穿桥<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1972\\10\\72af0404AA.JPG\">水洼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣裹邮包飞檐下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大妈家里念喜报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑谈祖国新变化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃花坞头读新闻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅起满田红浪花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农个个赞:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这姑娘的心连着咱。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支书也常把她夸:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老交通女儿真听党的话。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，乡邮员飞步阳光下——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张汗脸灼灼红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命青春放光华!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南汇县运输联社　胡天麟"}]}